

 command: link <who> 
 command: link <off>
 command: link <message>

 A player may establish a direct communication link with another player
 via the link command. To do this a player must first: link <name> and 
 the other person must accept the link. A link is then established until
 it is removed by either player or a player logs off. To remove a link
 you simply type "link off" or "link remove". Once the link has been
 establed simply "link <your message>" to talk. 

 
